node.text:
SKATE AND DESTROY CANCER! Get this shirt and watch the film to support @grindforlifeorg ! @kindhumans_movement created a tee that helps provide financial support for those fighting cancer and collaborated with @gopro on a rad film that tells Mike Roger's amazing story of beating cancer twice and starting this amazing org. 
Watch the full film on GoPro's youtube (LINK IN BIO), support at grindforlife.org and get the T-Shirt at kindhumans.com (LINK IN BIO)

#Kindhumans #GrindforLife #GoProForACause #CollabForKindness

node.text: @augie_days has been the bolts that have held my skateboarding together for decades, literally as the owner of Random skateboard hardware he has done so much for so many. Now my dear friend needs your help, let’s smash this goal for #AugieRodriguez and his beautiful family! Link is in my bio and story. We love you Augie 🤘🏼❤️🤘🏼

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Bucky Lasek on August 05, 2021. May be an image of car and outdoors.

node.text: Say hello to my @theproject_s5wrc carbon bodied GC Impreza. I haven’t decided exactly what I’m doing with it yet so I could be easily influenced by your comments below. All I do know at this point is I’m going to need help on this build. Hey @texas_dave @dustyy777 @derricthrone you have room for this one over there?! #subaru #subaruUSA #Impreza #rally #gymkhana #hillclimb #rallyready

node.text: I’ve made a long career out of falling down and getting back up. I used to carry ibuprofen in my skate bag aka skater skittles but now I’m stoked for the healthier option. Try @cbdmd.usa for your bumps and bruises and never slow down. Use code BUCKY to save 20% on your next order LINK IN BIO  #cbdmd #vertskateboarding #iloveskateboarding #KeepPushing

SKATE AND DESTROY CANCER! Get this shirt and watch the film to support @grindforlifeorg ! @kindhumans_movement created a tee that helps provide financial support for those fighting cancer and collaborated with @gopro on a rad film that tells Mike Roger's amazing story of beating cancer twice and starting this amazing org. 
Watch the full film on GoPro's youtube (LINK IN BIO), support at grindforlife.org and get the T-Shirt at kindhumans.com (LINK IN BIO)

#Kindhumans #GrindforLife #GoProForACause #CollabForKindness
